{"tid":1933504,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"★【全球攬炒】關廠規模是二次世界大戰以來從未見過","createTime":"2020-03-19T10:24:28.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-22T06:18:25.000Z","uid":19454,"like":11,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"4cfcfecbea70f8f902b9b1a443557f5ace18641a","tid":1933504,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-19T10:24:28.000Z","msg":"外國傳媒報道，新冠肺炎疫情衝擊已從服務業蔓延到製造業，重工業工廠紛紛關閉，有專家稱，關廠<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">規模是二次世界大戰以來從未見過</span></strong>。<br />\n<br />\n根據美國《國防生產法》，政府有權徵用、調度企業的原料、設備、人力等，白宮經濟顧問庫德洛透露，政府已與通用汽車和其他製造商討論，轉向生產呼吸器。在德國宣布汽車公司關閉兩周後，美國3大車廠通用、福特、快意佳士拿亦與工會同意關廠。<br />\n<br />\n密西根州汽車研究中心負責人Kristin Dziczek表示，現時每個地區、每個汽車廠都面臨停頓，近代歷史中沒有類似事件，二次世界大戰可能是最類近的例子。回看二戰時，工廠從生產汽車轉為生產坦克和槍，與現在重新調配和轉移生產的措施有相似之處。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/finance/20200319/bkn-20200319153221962-0319_00842_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Ffinance%2F20200319%2Fbkn-20200319153221962-0319_00842_001.html&d=vBgtTLCpkGvyAljQauEZFd%2BR0LtvndqJ8lr%2BzYsHiyM%3D&h=aa69122d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/finance/20200319/bkn-20200319153221962-0319_00842_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"2f16a62801d166bac1b34095e7134c182a3d6760","tid":1933504,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-19T10:24:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0131506e9c513f6cd0f9f978b8a7d6c06e15f881","tid":1933504,"uid":19454,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-